{
  "page": "Mazor Alexi",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> High King</span><br />Mazor Alexi</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Mazor_Alexi.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Mazor Alexi.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ab/Mazor_Alexi.jpg/300px-Mazor_Alexi.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"385\" srcset=\"/images/a/ab/Mazor_Alexi.jpg 1.5x\" /></a><div>Mazor Alexi as depicted in <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>: <i>Histories &amp; Lore</i>.</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/High_King_of_Sarnor\" title=\"High King of Sarnor\">High King of Sarnor</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Kingdom_of_Sarnor\" title=\"Kingdom of Sarnor\">Kingdom of Sarnor</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Tall_Men\" title=\"Tall Men\">Tall Men</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Sarnor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sarnor\">Sarnori</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Century_of_Blood\" title=\"Century of Blood\">Century of Blood</a><br />the <a href=\"/index.php/Field_of_Crows\" title=\"Field of Crows\">Field of Crows</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Mazor Alexi</b> was the last <a href=\"/index.php/High_King_of_Sarnor\" title=\"High King of Sarnor\">High King</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingdom_of_Sarnor\" title=\"Kingdom of Sarnor\">Kingdom of Sarnor</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mazor_Alexi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Prior to the fall of <a href=\"/index.php/Mardosh\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Mardosh\">Mardosh</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a>, the kings of the <a href=\"/index.php/Tall_Men\" title=\"Tall Men\">Sarnori</a> had remained divided. The destruction of the \"City of Soldiers\" and all its population led them to put aside their petty rivalries and ambitions, however, and unite under their <a href=\"/index.php/High_King_of_Sarnor\" title=\"High King of Sarnor\">High King</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Mazor Alexi assembled a great army from up and down the <a href=\"/index.php/Sarne\" title=\"Sarne\">Sarne</a> and struck out east. In the tall grass between <a href=\"/index.php/Sarnath\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sarnath\">Sarnath</a> and the ruins of <a href=\"/index.php/Kasath\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kasath\">Kasath</a>, the Tall Men faced four <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khalasar\" title=\"Khalasar\">khalasars</a></i>, with a combined might of eighty thousand horselords, in a battle that would be known as the <a href=\"/index.php/Field_of_Crows\" title=\"Field of Crows\">Field of Crows</a>. The Sarnori <a href=\"/index.php/Chariot\" title=\"Chariot\">chariots</a> smashed through the center of the Dothraki horse, killing Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Haro\" title=\"Haro\">Haro</a> and causing his <i>khalasar</i> to retreat. Alexi and his mounted cavalry plunged in after them, followed by the Sarnori foot. This was a trap, however, as the fleeing Dothraki turned and unleashed a storm of arrows. Meanwhile, the <i>khalasars</i> of Khals <a href=\"/index.php/Qano\" title=\"Qano\">Qano</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Zhako\" title=\"Zhako\">Zhako</a> swept in from north and south and Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Loso\" title=\"Loso\">Loso</a> and his screamers struck the Sarnori rear. Completely surrounded, Alexi's host was cut to pieces. A hundred thousand men died, Mazor Alexi among them.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mazor_Alexi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Free Cities: The Grasslands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404101120\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.093 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.338 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 620/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10474/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5862/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1289/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1462/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.230/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.56 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  325.076      1 -total\n 97.03%  315.431      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 96.56%  313.890      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.68%   37.962     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  4.80%   15.592      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.33%    7.579      3 Template:Ref\n  1.32%    4.288      3 Template:Ref/core\n  0.55%    1.779      1 Template:References\n  0.51%    1.642      3 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:19551-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404101120 and revision id 323016\n -->\n",
